question: Analyze the trend of Healthy Life Expectancy At Birth by region (Asia, Europe, North America)
query: SELECT    regional_indicator,    AVG(healthy_life_expectancy_at_birth) AS avg_healthy_life_expectancy,    year FROM    world_happiness_report WHERE    regional_indicator IN ('Asia', 'Europe', 'North America') GROUP BY    regional_indicator, year ORDER BY    regional_indicator, year LIMIT 50;
